.TH LOOTSHEET-QUEST-WRITEOFF 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-quest-writeoff \\- Write off an uncollectible quest reward
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet quest writeoff [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet quest writeoff --id ID --date YYYY-MM-DD [--description TEXT]

Example:
  lootsheet quest writeoff --id quest-123 --date 2026-04-20 --description "Patron vanished into the Feywild"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--date=string
write-off date in YYYY-MM-DD (required) (default: )
.TP
--description=string
optional description (default: )
.TP
-h, --help
help for writeoff
.TP
--id=string
quest ID (required) (default: )
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-quest(1)
